{"article_id":"SEcLMntXPhlBy4yw","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump tore into Jeff Sessions in an interview","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"published Wednesday ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"going so far as to say","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"\" I don ' t have an attorney general \"","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"-- although he appeared to later soften the statement .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"In an interview with The Hill , Trump said","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"the beleagured Sessions was absent","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"and performing poorly in his role as the nation ' s top lawyer .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"\" I don ' t have an attorney general .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"It ' s very sad , \"","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Trump ' s relationship has long been strained with Sessions","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"since the former Alabama senator recused himself from the Russia investigation in early 2017 .","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"While Sessions was the first senator","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"to back Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and has been central in passing key planks of Trump ' s agenda","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"-- particularly on border enforcement and law and order --","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Trump has repeatedly slammed him publicly .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"In the latest interview , Trump said","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"his frustration extends beyond the Russia recusal .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"\" I ' m not happy at the border ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"I ' m not happy with numerous things , not just this , \"","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Trump went on to say","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that Sessions \" did very poorly \"","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and \" was mixed up and confused \" during his confirmation hearing .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"But Trump also returned back to slamming Sessions on his decision","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"to recuse himself","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"-- which Sessions said","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"was required by DOJ regulations due to his participation in the Trump campaign .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"GREGG JARRETT :","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"AG SESSIONS 'WILL BE FIRED ' AFTER MIDTERMS DUE TO CARTER PAGE SURVEILLANCE","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"\" He gets in","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"and probably because of the experience","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"that he had","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"going through the nominating","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"when somebody asked him the first question about Hillary Clinton or something","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"' I recuse myself ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"I recuse myself , ' ''","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Trump said .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"On Wednesday , Trump was asked about the interview by reporters at the White House ,","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"he was `` disappointed '' with Sessions","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"-- although he seemed to walk back his earlier remarks .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"`` I 'm disappointed in the attorney general for numerous reasons","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"but we have an attorney general --","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"I 'm disappointed in the attorney general for many reasons","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"and you understand that , ''","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"he said","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"before traveling to North Carolina","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"to survey Hurricane Florence damage .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Trump has in the past indicated","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"that he intends to fire Sessions .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"In August he tweeted a quote from Sen. Lindsey Graham , R-S.C. ,","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"who said on \" Fox News @ Night \"","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"that the AG serves \" at the pleasure of the President . \"","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"\" Every President deserves an Attorney General","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"they have confidence in , \"","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Graham said .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"\" I believe","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"every President has a right to their Cabinet ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"these are not lifetime appointments .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"You serve at the pleasure of the President . \"","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"TRUMP CLAIMS","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"SESSIONS 'DOES N'T UNDERSTAND","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"WHAT IS HAPPENING ' IN JUSTICE DEPT .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"But Trump has not indicated","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"that such a move is imminent ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"and he could struggle to get a replacement through the Senate","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"depending on what happens in the November midterms .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"In August , Trump said in an interview with Fox & Friends","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"that Sessions had \" never taken control \" of his department .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"\" But when everybody sees what ' s going on in the Justice Department","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"-- I always put ' justice ' now with quotes --","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"it ' s a very , very sad day .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Jeff Sessions recused himself ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"which he shouldn ' t have done .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Or he should have told me , \"","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"\" Even my enemies say","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that Jeff Sessions should have told you","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"that he was going to recuse himself","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"and then you wouldn ' t have put him in .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"He took the job","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"and then he said","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"I ' m going to recuse myself .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"I said ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"' what kind of a man is this ? ' \"","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"RUBIO ASKS DOJ TO DETERMINE","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"IF KERRY VIOLATED FEDERAL LAWS MEETING WITH IRANIAN OFFICIALS","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"\" I took control of the Department of Justice the day","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"I was sworn in ,","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"which is why we have had unprecedented success","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"at effectuating the President ' s agenda","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"one","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"hat protects the safety and security rights of the American people ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"educes violent crime ,","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"nforces our immigration laws ,","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"romotes economic growth ,","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"nd advances religious liberty . \"","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"e went on to say ,","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"While I am Attorney General ,","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"he actions of the Department of Justice will not be improperly influenced by political considerations .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":209,"left":134,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":115,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":109,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":106,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":114,"left":111,"right":113,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":111,"left":5,"right":110,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":110,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":112,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nucle